Personal Growth#

Participation in WISE Living & Learning Village#

For my first three semesters at NCSU, I chose to live and participate in the Women in Science and Engineering Living and Learning Village. I lived and connected with with other women who were passionate about engineering and the sciences, and have been grateful for this experience throughout my undergraduate career.
